Exactly.

23:39.115 --> 23:39.876
That would be wonderful.

23:40.237 --> 23:40.738
That would be wonderful.

23:40.758 --> 23:41.078
You know?

23:42.140 --> 23:44.304
You and I are formulating this right now.

23:44.324 --> 23:50.676
