24:38.090 --> 24:38.570
Yeah.

24:38.731 --> 24:40.152
Whenever we're on this stuff.

24:40.172 --> 24:41.514
Ah, yes, I understand.

24:41.534 --> 24:42.154
You're well trained.

24:42.174 --> 24:42.495
Thanks.

